# Cloudflare Pages _redirects file for SPA routing

# 重要：顺序很关键，特定的路由应该放在通用路由之前
# Important: Order matters, specific routes should be before generic ones

# 将 /priv/xxx/note 和 /priv/xxx 路径都重定向到 index.html，保持 URL 不变，状态码 200
# Redirect both /priv/xxx/note and /priv/xxx paths to index.html, preserving the URL, status code 200
/priv/*/note    /index.html   200
/priv/*         /index.html   200

# 将所有其他路径重定向到 index.html，保持 URL 不变，状态码 200
# Redirect all other paths to index.html, preserving the URL, status code 200
/*              /index.html   200
